summary: An ordinance relating to the improvement of The Alley in Block 41, Gilman's Addition, being the alley between 12th Avenue West and 13th Avenue West from Ruffner Street to West Bertona Street and certain other streets, avenues, and alleys by paving and otherwise improving the same, at authorized by Ordinance No. 82808 creating Local Improvement District No. 6057, and amending Section 2 of said Ordinance to provide for additional funds.
